             :documentation <https://hyperbrowser.uio.no/gsuite/static/hyperbrowser/gsuite/GSuite_specification.html> ,
                            <https://hyperbrowser.uio.no/gsuite/static/hyperbrowser/gsuite/GSuite_specification.txt> ;
