                          "Information sensitivity" ,
                          "Personal data" ,
                          "Private data" ,
                          "Sensitive data" ,
                          "Sensitive human data" ,
                          "Sensitive information" ,
                          "Special category data" ;
            oboInOwl:hasDefinition "Data protection is a topic concerning data that should be protected from disclosure, damage, or unauthorised access, due to its sensitive nature." ;
            oboInOwl:hasRelatedSynonym "Management of sensitive data" ;
            oboInOwl:inSubset :bio ,
                              :topics ;
            oboInOwl:savedBy "Matúš Kalaš" ,
                             "bianchini" ;
            rdfs:comment "Note that the term information security (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Information_security) covers both the data management aspect for protected data (this topic_4044), and the technical aspect of cybersecurity (topic_4045)." ,
                         "Sensitive data includes not only personal and commercial data, but also information about e.g. localisation of endangered biological species that could be exploited." ;
            rdfs:label "Data protection" ;
